{"tid":1180965,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伯明翰一小學發生穆斯林與LGBT示威對抗，最高法院禁止雙方在附近示威","createTime":"2019-06-01T08:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T09:38:51.000Z","uid":64191,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3137254ee5442017ac463fe56d24f7166709b2d4","tid":1180965,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T08:47:55.000Z","msg":"Protesters against LGBT teaching at a primary school have been banned from gathering outside the gates by a High Court injunction.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-birmingham-48480299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-birmingham-48480299&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbRA11HdiY488GD%2FHa51CVEA%3D&h=eca87ed6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-birmingham-48480299</a><br />\n<br />\n件事係咁既，伯明翰有間小學教LGBT，引黎一班穆斯林家長反對，聚集校門外抗議，幾個星期後學校基於壓力撤銷。<br />\n<br />\n但係，一班LGBT支持者到場報置海報對抗，惹黎憤怒既穆斯林示威者掟雞蛋反擊，更警告下次會掟磚。<br />\n<br />\n結果最高法院頒布禁令，禁止穆斯林家長響學校周圍抗議、禁止抗議者發放宣傳單張，然後開放6月10日上訴<br />\n<br />\n然而呢次衝突，左膠都係睇唔到既，只係諗要用咩侵侵氣球示威。"},{"pid":"3799ab391199280ef86e986b7976c7e660d950a6","tid":1180965,"uid":89063,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T08:54:31.000Z","msg":"一班唔接受西方文明嘅野蠻人偏偏移民西方國家係咁生蛋，左膠同時為佢地造保護傘⋯⋯睇唔透"},{"pid":"722822bf8f12c4cc8691c267352ae24215408d77","tid":1180965,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:36:36.000Z","msg":"小學就要學？！教用condom都無咁早教呀？"},{"pid":"085857b71d262e8c00a0b83953601e464f06acd2","tid":1180965,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:38:51.000Z","msg":"回教徒返中東啦"}]}